IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. eval.
       AUTHOR. CHRIS.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
         WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
         01 VAL1 PIC X(2) VALUE SPACES.
         01 PACKAGE-TYPE PIC X(1) VALUE SPACE.
         01 BASE PIC 9(3) VALUE ZEROS.
         01 RATE PIC 9(3) VALUE ZERO.
         01 TOTAL PIC 9(3) VALUE ZEROS.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MOVE 'A' TO PACKAGE-TYPE.
       MOVE 010 TO BASE.
       MOVE 5 TO RATE.
       EVALUATE PACKAGE-TYPE 
           WHEN 'A' MOVE 20 TO BASE
           WHEN 'B' MOVE 10 TO BASE
           WHEN 'C' MOVE 5 TO BASE
       END-EVALUATE.
       MULTIPLY BASE BY RATE GIVING TOTAL
         SIZE ERROR DISPLAY 'SIZE ERROR ON TOTAL COMPUTATION.'
       END-MULTIPLY.
       DISPLAY VAL1.
       DISPLAY PACKAGE-TYPE.
       DISPLAY BASE.
       DISPLAY RATE.
       DISPLAY TOTAL.
       STOP RUN.
